OL,5, Amazon workers will stage the          
OL,6, first-ever UK strike against the online
OL,7, giant on Wednesday in a protest over   
OL,8, pay.                                   
OL,10,FMembers of the GMB union are walking   
OL,11,Fout at Amazon's Coventry warehouse over
OL,12,Fwhat they call a "derisory" 50p an hour
OL,13,Fpay rise.                              
OL,15,FWorkers told the BBC about "severe"    
OL,16,Fconditions, claiming they are          
OL,17,Fconstantly monitored and upbraided for 
OL,18,F"idle time" lasting just a few minutes.
OL,20,FAmazon said it has a system "that      
OL,21,Frecognises great performance".         
